advancement.mythicmetals.root.title: Mythic Metals
advancement.mythicmetals.root.descriptio: Discover all the ores deep underground
advancement.mythicmetals.unobtainium.des: Obtain Unobtainium, usually found deeply surrounded by deepslate
advancement.mythicmetals.adamantite.desc: Find Adamantite in the deepest part of the Deep Dark
advancement.mythicmetals.mythril.title: Dwarven Treasure
advancement.mythicmetals.mythril.descrip: Find Mythril in the upper part of the Deep Dark
advancement.mythicmetals.orichalcum.desc: Find Orichalcum scattered around the Deep Dark
advancement.mythicmetals.hallowed.title: Sacred Alloy
advancement.mythicmetals.hallowed.descri: Forge a Hallowed Bar with a high tier forge, using the ores from the Deep Dark
advancement.mythicmetals.carmot.title: Alchemical Miracle
advancement.mythicmetals.carmot.descript: Find Carmot around the top of the Deepslate layer
advancement.mythicmetals.aquarium.title: Underwater Expeditions
advancement.mythicmetals.osmium.title: When Can I Make a Windmill?
advancement.mythicmetals.osmium.descript: Find Osmium high up in the mountains
advancement.mythicmetals.banglum.title: Legendary Bang
advancement.mythicmetals.banglum.descrip: Find Banglum, the first stepping stone towards other metals
advancement.mythicmetals.kyber.title: I thought this was a Crystal?
advancement.mythicmetals.kyber.descripti: Find Kyber, usually hidden inside Amethyst Geodes
advancement.mythicmetals.starrite.title: Fallen Stardrops
advancement.mythicmetals.starrite.descri: Find Starrite, an abundant crystal usually found in The End
advancement.mythicmetals.star_platinum.d: Forge Star Platinum from Starrite, Platinum, and Carmot
advancement.mythicmetals.celestium.title: Unstoppable Force
advancement.mythicmetals.celestium.descr: Forge Celestium from Star Platinum, Kyber, and Unobtainium
advancement.mythicmetals.metallurgium.de: Forge Metallurgium from Hallowed, Palladium, and Unobtainium
advancement.mythicmetals.stormyx.title: Diamonds from the Nether
advancement.mythicmetals.stormyx.descrip: Find Stormyx hiding deep below the Netherrack and Blackstone
advancement.mythicmetals.durasteel.title: From a Galaxy, far far away...
advancement.mythicmetals.durasteel.descr: Forge Durasteel, a better steel made from Quadrillum and Manganese
advancement.mythicmetals.midas_gold.desc: Find Midas Gold in the nether, which can forge any ore into gold
advancement.mythicmetals.prometheum.desc: Find Prometheum deep in Jungles or Lush Caves
advancement.mythicmetals.palladium.title: The Hottest Beans
advancement.mythicmetals.palladium.descr: Find Palladium around the lava ocean in the Nether
